        "subject": "LU-957 scrub: Ancillary work for LFSCK/OI scrub",
        "message": "LU-957 scrub: Ancillary work for LFSCK/OI scrub\n\nBackport of commit I8b1f1f1160db25ce05bd2d5688f9ff1507e3841b.\n\n1) New debug sub-system - 'D_LFSCK'\nFor Lustre fsck/scrub running trace.\n\n2) New MDT mount option - 'noscrub'\nTo disable auto triggering OI scrub when MDT mounts up\nor by RPC which accesses inconsistent OI mapping entry.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <laisiyao@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I22046a89a712cc3544187ea9fb6f26aa364b2fdf\n"
      },
